Project.Title: Functional analysis of microsomal proteins
Project.Description: Protein correlation profiling to identified the oligomerization state of cholate solubilized microsomal proteins.

Relation.Keywords: Protein correlation profiling, Arabidopsis, Membrane-associated, protein complexes

Sample.title: Sucrose Velocity Gradient Profiling
Sample.note: The P200 was separated on a linear sucrose velocity gradient of 22 -52%.

Fractionation.title: Microsomal fraction
Fractionation.note: By differential centrifugation the microsomal fraction was enriched by pelleting chloroplast by centrigation a 1 k x g for 10 minutes. The Supernatant was transferred to an ultra-centrifuge were it was pelleted by spinning at 200 k x g for 20 minutes

Fractionation.title: Microsomal fraction
